Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼殺隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是玩樂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你這種垃圾就該被肅清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻肅清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,別給我小看鬼殺隊
