Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,禰豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.08,zhu,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.45,zhu,,0,0,0,,禰豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.84,zhu,,0,0,0,,善逸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,您的衣服好像很髒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給您洗乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,請先換上這件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這衣服觸感很好 穿著很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,晚飯吃天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,對 是那個裹著一層麵粉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
